          <text xml:lang="en" index="3"></text>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="4">- Market activities cannot have a geographical location that does not fully contain the geographical locations of its supplying transforming activities: exchange 'inorganic nitrogen fertiliser, as N' is supplied by 'urea ammonium nitrate production, RER, 1999 - 1999' which has an overlapping geography not fully contained in geography of dataset.exchange 'inorganic nitrogen fertiliser, as N' is supplied by 'ammonium nitrate phosphate production, RER, 1999 - 1999' which has an overlapping geography not fully contained in geography of dataset.exchange 'inorganic nitrogen fertiliser, as N' is supplied by 'treatment, sludge from pulp and paper production, landfarming, Europe without Switzerland, 2011 - 2012' which has an overlapping geography not fully contained in geography of dataset.exchange 'inorganic nitrogen fertiliser, as N' is supplied by 'calcium ammonium nitrate production, RER, 1999 - 1999' which has an overlapping geography not fully contained in geography of dataset.exchange 'inorganic nitrogen fertiliser, as N' is supplied by 'diammonium phosphate production, RER, 1999 - 1999' which has an overlapping geography not fully contained in geography of dataset.exchange 'inorganic nitrogen fertiliser, as N' is supplied by 'monoammonium phosphate production, RER, 1999 - 1999' which has an overlapping geography not fully contained in geography of dataset.exchange 'inorganic nitrogen fertiliser, as N' is supplied by 'heat production, straw, at furnace 300kW, RER, 1983 - 2007' which has an overlapping geography not fully contained in geography of dataset.exchange 'inorganic nitrogen fertiliser, as N' is supplied by 'heat production, straw, organic, at furnace 300kW, RER, 1983 - 2007' which has an overlapping geography not fully contained in geography of dataset.</text>
